channel.title: Projekt_Majem - Looking for collab/have several 1 minute preview to choose from
channel.description:
Hey guys,
I'm Looking to collaborate with someone with a bit more experience to take it to the next level. Have several one minute previews of my most current tracks posted to my public/unrestricted Instagram page (https://www.instagram.com/projekt_majem). DM me if you see something you can work with - I have lyrics for a few too, so a good voice would also be welcomed!
Cheers J
